        <h2>Mobile &amp; Wireless Expert Witness — Wi-Fi, Cellular &amp; 5G</h2>

        <div class="two-col-text-img">
          <div>
            <p>Billions of <a href="/us-10598764-radar-target-detection-and-imaging-system-for-autonomous-car/">mobile wireless</a> devices are deployed using <a href="/us-20180130102-reliable-rating-system-and-method-thereof/">wireless</a> technologies. As a <a href="/">telecommunications expert witness</a> and <a href="/communications-expert-witness/internet-expert-witness/">internet expert witness</a>, Dr. Lavian applies academic research and hands-on industry experience to mobile wireless expert witness work, combining technical knowledge of patent issues with subject matter expertise.</p>

            <p>His background covers mobile wireless systems, devices, and networks. Dr. Lavian has extensive experience with the relationships between wireless applications and their underlying <a href="/us-10348313-radar-target-detection-system/">communications</a> service architectures, designs, and implementations.</p>
          </div>
          <div>
